}

###
### POST ENDPOINTS (Jersey Listings)
###

### Get all posts
# Fetches all jersey posts from the database
# Returns array with user info (sub-schema), jerseyDetails, likes array, commentsCount
# Includes timestamps (createdAt, updatedAt) for paging support
GET https://localhost:5000/api/post
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VyIjp7ImlkIjoiNjlhMTRmNTk5NDRjNThhMDYxOTI0Y2I1In0sImlhdCI6MTc3MjU2MTQ3NywiZXhwIjoxNzcyNTY1MDc3fQ.5g7rgyTJODxyhr1OcswrDpmuEX9FzrMtRkfmN2VKaFM

###

### Get single post by ID
# Retrieves a specific post with all details including user, jersey, and engagement metrics
# Replace :postId with actual MongoDB ObjectId from created post response
GET https://localhost:5000/api/post/69a6e523cd08f2fa3c448925
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VyIjp7ImlkIjoiNjlhMTRmNTk5NDRjNThhMDYxOTI0Y2I1In0sImlhdCI6MTc3MjU2MTQ3NywiZXhwIjoxNzcyNTY1MDc3fQ.5g7rgyTJODxyhr1OcswrDpmuEX9FzrMtRkfmN2VKaFM

###

### Create a new jersey post
# Creates a post with text description, optional image, and full jerseyDetails object
# jerseyDetails MUST include: team, league, price (Number), size (XS/S/M/L/XL/XXL), imageUrl
# User sub-schema is automatically embedded from JWT token - you only provide text and jerseyDetails!
    POST https://localhost:5000/api/post
    Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VyIjp7ImlkIjoiNjlhMTRmNTk5NDRjNThhMDYxOTI0Y2I1In0sImlhdCI6MTc3MjU2MTQ3NywiZXhwIjoxNzcyNTY1MDc3fQ.5g7rgyTJODxyhr1OcswrDpmuEX9FzrMtRkfmN2VKaFM
    Content-Type: application/json

    {
      "text": "Selling authentic Hapoel-Tel-Aviv 2023-24 season jersey. Excellent condition, never worn. Original tags still attached.",
      "image": "/uploads/post-photos/manchester-united-2024.jpg",
      "jerseyDetails": {
        "team": "HTA",
        "league": "ISR League",
        "price": 100.99,
        "size": "XL",
        "imageUrl": "/uploads/jerseys/Hapoel-Tel-Aviv-2023-24.jpg"
      }
    }

###

### Create a new post with image (multipart/form-data)
# Creates a post with an uploaded image file attached
# Image file is automatically saved to back/uploads/ with unique name
# Returns the image path as /uploads/{unique-filename}
# IMPORTANT: Replace YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE with actual token from login!
POST https://localhost:5000/api/post
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VyIjp7ImlkIjoiNjlhMTRmNTk5NDRjNThhMDYxOTI0Y2I1In0sImlhdCI6MTc3MjU2MTQ3NywiZXhwIjoxNzcyNTY1MDc3fQ.5g7rgyTJODxyhr1OcswrDpmuEX9FzrMtRkfmN2VKaFM
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="text"

Here is my vintage HTA FC jersey from the 2007. Official made, still in excellent condition with minimal wear. Unmatched collectible piece!
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="Hapoel-jersey-2000s.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="jerseyDetails"

{
  "team": "HTA FC",
  "league": "ISR League",
  "price": 125.50,
  "size": "M",
  "imageUrl": "/uploads/jerseys/HTA-2000s.jpg"
}
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="new_jersey_photo.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

