This is the updated text with everything fixed!
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="jerseyDetails"

{
  "team": "Real Madrid",
  "league": "La Liga",
  "price": 120,
  "size": "L",
  "imageUrl": "/uploads/jerseys/real-madrid-home.jpg"
}
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
